data.rationale:
This module is to be a replacement for Net::CDDB. Net::CDDB's
    author (Jeremy D. Zawodny: jzawodn@users.sourceforge.net) should be
    available to verify this. The namespace was chosen to stand in-place
    with Net::CDDB.
